OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775049066
OL,3,CTerrier rescued from rabbit hole after
OL,4,Ctwo days thanks to volunteers
OL,6,FA 14-year-old terrier named Mole spent
OL,7,Ftwo days trapped underground in a
OL,8,Frabbit warren before being rescued by
OL,9,Fvolunteers.
OL,11,FMole's owners, who live near Bruton,
OL,12,Fin Somerset, said they contacted
OL,13,FSearch and Scan, a charity run by
OL,14,Fvolunteers that helps find missing
OL,15,Fpets, after she didn't return when she
OL,16,Fwas called.
OL,18,FAfter 48 hours, the volunteers managed
OL,19,Fto track Mole down using cameras and a
OL,20,Fdrone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
