OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775049066
OL,3,CTerrier rescued from rabbit hole after
OL,4,Ctwo days thanks to volunteers
OL,6,FZara D'Abo, Mole's owner, said: "She
OL,7,Fwas in some rabbit warrens up on the
OL,8,Ftop of a hill where we're clearing
OL,9,Fsome land. She's gone down a few
OL,10,Frabbit holes before, but she's never
OL,11,Fgot stuck.
OL,13,F"I burst into tears when we heard the
OL,14,Fnews. I was so relieved."
OL,16,FJo Southway, one of the founders of
OL,17,FSearch and Scan, said they get called
OL,18,Fout to help find missing pets every
OL,19,Fday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
