OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775049066
OL,3,CTerrier rescued from rabbit hole after
OL,4,Ctwo days thanks to volunteers
OL,6,FShe said they were about to abandon
OL,7,Fthe search for Mole when they heard
OL,8,Fher whimpering, and were able to
OL,9,Ffigure out which burrow she was in
OL,10,Fusing cameras and drones.
OL,12,F"As soon as we knew she was
OL,13,Funderground, we worked out she had
OL,14,Fgone to a rabbit hole, and she had got
OL,15,Fstuck," Ms Southway said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
