FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775049066
OL,3,CTerrier rescued from rabbit hole after
OL,4,Ctwo days thanks to volunteers
OL,6,F"We had to dig down, but the issue is
OL,7,Fyou don't want to injure the dog. At
OL,8,Ffirst, we started with a spade, then
OL,9,Fwhen we thought we were getting close,
OL,10,Fanother volunteer, Nick, started
OL,11,Fdigging with his bare hands.
OL,13,F"In the process, he actually broke his
OL,14,Ffinger, but he still kept digging!"
OL,16,FMs Southway said it took four hours to
OL,17,Fget Mole out before she was reunited
OL,18,Fwith her owners.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
