CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775049066
OL,3,CTerrier rescued from rabbit hole after
OL,4,Ctwo days thanks to volunteers
OL,6,FMs D'Abo said: "She was quite clingy
OL,7,Fat first when she came out, but she's
OL,8,Fdefinitely got more spring in her step
OL,9,Fnow.
OL,11,F"She's very determined, tenacious, as
OL,12,Fyou'd expect all terriers to be. She's
OL,13,Fa good creature."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
